  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #132213

  26 May 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> kopete-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  25 May 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> kopete-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Stable on x86 wrt bug #132213

  22 May 2006; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> -kopete-3.4.1.ebuild:
  Remove 3.4.1 for GLSA 200607-23

