*kopete-3.5.2 (22 Mar 2006)

  22 Mar 2006; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> +kopete-3.5.2.ebuild:
  KDE 3.5.2. Not yet released upstream, and so package.masked for now.

  07 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> kopete-3.5.1-r1.ebuild:
